context: The chapter house and Pyx Chamber at Westminster Abbey are in the guardianship of <a0_0><b3_0><b4_0>English Heritage<b4_0/><b3_0/><a0_0/>, but under the care and management of <a1_0><b6_0>the <b5_0>Dean and Chapter of Westminster<b6_0/><b5_0/><a1_0/>. English Heritage have funded a major programme of work on the chapter house, comprising <a2_0><b7_0>repairs<b7_0/><a2_0/> to the roof, gutters, stonework on the elevations and flying buttresses as well as repairs to the lead light.
